body_html:
That's odd. I'll try to reproduce and debug this. I also saw your comment on my PR. Are you still having that issue as well?

By the way, would it be possible to merge #1289 first? That way, we can update the protobuf dependency more easy since all we would need to do is update the WORKSPACE file rather than having to update the submodule reference. The failures in the last CI run on #1289 don't seem to be related to that PR.
